The Threat Manager feature allows an application to control security threats a device actively monitors and how it responds.

## Main Functionality

* Enable/Disable Threat Detection
* Perform Counter Measures when a Threat is Detected
* Perform Periodic Scans of root-based threats
* Set a custom interval for Periodic Scans
* Define specific folders to monitor for threats

